{"tid":2140812,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"好想養貓","createTime":"2020-08-05T08:46:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-23T03:15:21.000Z","uid":341973,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"421861833a2df618b85c682d97433d9b131b4712","tid":2140812,"uid":341973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T08:46:29.000Z","msg":"又細到大都好鐘意貓 同屋企人已經講咗好耐 <br />\n宜家終於應承比我養一隻貓<br />\n<br />\n勢估唔到 過咗屋企人嗰關之後又要過貓義工呢關<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我明，將隻貓貓交俾人領養 佢哋都要好小心把關 <br />\n但態度可唔可以好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n貓b成日都要一對養 成貓又會考慮有經驗人士先<br />\n廿五歲以上先可以領養<br />\n已讀不回 領養要求又多<br />\n其實養貓最緊要係肯花時間同照顧佢一生 <br />\n咁多條件加埋啲咁嘅態度<br />\n其實真係搞到有心領養嘅人會好撚灰<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但因為之前睇片見到啲仆街繁殖埸點對啲貓 太深刻 所以真係唔係好想買貓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以想問吓有冇巴絲係成功領養到貓？同埋邊度領養<br />\n唉。有冇好嘅貓義工<br />\n我真係好想好想養貓 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7c8f7bf8ad2c32b028abdcfb3929f5491c8723f","tid":2140812,"uid":201414,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:02:38.000Z","msg":"班義貓工霸撚曬啲貓 領養又要乜乜柒柒 根本係有心玩鳩想領養果班人 屌你老母貓義工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9510e7b62f3322e1f70870bd55db001ed57b9209","tid":2140812,"uid":32577,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T10:35:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我領養第一隻貓好輕鬆，齊野再見埋貓貓第日就帶得走<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />宜家想搵多隻，啲人成日已讀不回，我都廢事追佢"},{"pid":"b3f282b8bbfeef37df4925a65cb1ed1dd98791eb","tid":2140812,"uid":53122,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T10:38:58.000Z","msg":"班貓異工全部痴線<br />\n<br />\n去買唔駛受氣"},{"pid":"11ea3149488b1900d950f15746f59902a8ffbc09","tid":2140812,"uid":140113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T10:47:37.000Z","msg":"SPCA幫到你<br />\n不過要夠快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"172e3926314bd4104d3fef5a5476d16d3457cfa3","tid":2140812,"uid":141358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T12:02:23.000Z","msg":"貓義工死全家啦"},{"pid":"2695171d8d07ef57ef4dbd2e34525253e7ad7101","tid":2140812,"uid":32577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"11ea3149488b1900d950f15746f59902a8ffbc09","tid":2140812,"uid":140113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T10:47:37.000Z","msg":"SPCA幫到你<br />\n不過要夠快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T12:28:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪po 得上網既9成都俾人認左頭<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />次次有新貓都係hold 左"},{"pid":"f5c044732b5f79f14d539c7383c58035dbe2de44","tid":2140812,"uid":341973,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"11ea3149488b1900d950f15746f59902a8ffbc09","tid":2140812,"uid":140113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T10:47:37.000Z","msg":"SPCA幫到你<br />\n不過要夠快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T12:47:18.000Z","msg":"我會多啲留意吓SPCA 希望今次可以領養到貓貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f583297c6b586b27eb75f85df2da2fea3080bb0d","tid":2140812,"uid":21752,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T12:53:08.000Z","msg":"我算好彩 屋企兩隻都係分別唔同朋友到拎返來<br />\n一隻係朋友屋企隻貓生貓BB 佢問有冇人想養 跟住我買齊貓用品 屋企環境準備好哂就直接抱得貓返去<br />\n另一隻就係朋友住村屋 平時日日都會準備一大堆貓糧 每日定時定候啲野貓就會來食 咁啱嗰陣有幾隻兩三個月嘅貓仔會跟埋去食 個朋友就問有冇人肯養 好過佢地通山跑做野貓<br />\n本身最初都係諗住搵呢啲咩貓義工 但班友真係好撚麻煩 又以為自己高人一等咁<br />\n之前亦都見過有case係領養完之後 俾啲貓義工日日騷擾 所以最後都係冇去搵貓義工領養"},{"pid":"95c2bbc5973af2e69661929bd2e8d866e089545f","tid":2140812,"uid":51196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T12:54:33.000Z","msg":"買啦"},{"pid":"9ffd82e696071c3498a824b48f34e55c83178e32","tid":2140812,"uid":341973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2695171d8d07ef57ef4dbd2e34525253e7ad7101","tid":2140812,"uid":32577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"11ea3149488b1900d950f15746f59902a8ffbc09","tid":2140812,"uid":140113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T10:47:37.000Z","msg":"SPCA幫到你<br />\n不過要夠快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T12:28:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪po 得上網既9成都俾人認左頭<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />次次有新貓都係hold 左"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T12:54:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係 但我見啲人話hold咗都可以照留意吓同申請 <br />\n可能遲啲打去問問 希望領養到"},{"pid":"a4bbeab2c7ef14f76c9d3e5204be4c92ab35bd4f","tid":2140812,"uid":341973,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f583297c6b586b27eb75f85df2da2fea3080bb0d","tid":2140812,"uid":21752,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T12:53:08.000Z","msg":"我算好彩 屋企兩隻都係分別唔同朋友到拎返來<br />\n一隻係朋友屋企隻貓生貓BB 佢問有冇人想養 跟住我買齊貓用品 屋企環境準備好哂就直接抱得貓返去<br />\n另一隻就係朋友住村屋 平時日日都會準備一大堆貓糧 每日定時定候啲野貓就會來食 咁啱嗰陣有幾隻兩三個月嘅貓仔會跟埋去食 個朋友就問有冇人肯養 好過佢地通山跑做野貓<br />\n本身最初都係諗住搵呢啲咩貓義工 但班友真係好撚麻煩 又以為自己高人一等咁<br />\n之前亦都見過有case係領養完之後 俾啲貓義工日日騷擾 所以最後都係冇去搵貓義工領養"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T13:00:00.000Z","msg":"好羨慕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我身邊朋友啲貓貓已經絕左育 所以唔會有貓bb<br />\n領養真係好講緣份 <br />\n唉 希望之後可以領養到貓仔"},{"pid":"a087d9f0efc1a9e5ebd620976ba2e92b5a9cede9","tid":2140812,"uid":341973,"lik